Romi’adan no cikiw i hekal (ikilis: Earth Day) pasetek to mihecahecaan 4 folad 22 romi’ad, 

o kalonohekalan to pidipot to pala a demak. Sa’ayaway demak romi’ad no cikiw i 1970 miheca i Amilika a pitilidan mapalowad kina pidipot to pala a onto,

1990 miheca onini a demak nai Amilika pasayra i hekal, malakapolongan no midipotay to pala no hekal a romi’adan ato pisintingan pidipot to pala a romi’ad, toni a romi’ad kasasiromaroma no kitakit a tamdaw kasasiroma a pisinting ato sapilaheciaw to pidipot to pala a nihiratengan.

